    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em> You can use mental power to modulate the roiling energies within your soul.</em></p><p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Animus pool or equivalent ability (such as a rubato bard's tempo class feature or the Tap Animus feat).</p><p><strong>Benefit</strong>: When initiating maneuvers with a psionic augment, you may spend points of animus as if they were power points. In addition, you gain a reserve of 1 power point and the psionic subtype, allowing you to take psionic feats, metapsionic feats, and psionic item creation feats, and to gain psionic focus.</p>",
